title: Cempaka Ratu Rumah Makan
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Ovo, International, Organic, Western, Juice bar, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Indonesian, Non-veg
description:
Serves meat, veg options available. Simple open air restaurant located in front of the Indian ocean with view over the whole bay.
Has indoor and outside seating, on the beach, and 4 bamboo gazebos. Menu is vegetarian and vegan friendly and kitchen will accommodate special dietary requests with advance notice. Salads, omlettes, bamboo stew served with rice, cream of life (fermented cashew and coconut), and others.
streetAddress: Cempaka Ratu Rumah Makan Resort, Pelabuan Ratu
